Summary
=======
x11-touch-mouse is a utility to transform touch screen events into simulated
X11 mouse events. It is intended for use on Kobo eReaders running X11 in an
Alpine Linux chroot.

Usage:
   x11-touch-mouse /dev/input/event1

x11-touch-mouse needs to run as root to be able to read the
devices.

For more information, see the x11-touch-mouse(1) man page.

